Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:02.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're challenging 100?! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:09.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't set up for one \Nperson to destroy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The competition for day three is Pandemonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:56.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a contest to see who can slay the \Nmost out of 100 magic-generated monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The contestants enter one at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:01.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and indicate the number of \Nmonsters they aim to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They get points by successfully \Nbeating the beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:07.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is to repeatedly rotate \Nthrough the players, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All 100 will be my opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I exercise my right to challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...100!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:25.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This beyond-foolhardy challenge \Nis about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100 to 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside is pretty big...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's upside down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick just lookin' at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:55.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Erza Scarlet from Fairy Tail A.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch have come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:16.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the D-class ones looked \Nreally strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she really mean to take \Nall of them on by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She does. Erza means it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were a better fit for \Nthis than that Chariot event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Erza-san be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll get through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it should be a spectacle, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's as reckless as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't changed a bit \Nin the past seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blumenblatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Erza has carried out a preemptive \Nstrike with an omni-directional attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The D-class monsters are \Ndropping one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she trying to demolish them all at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing an omni-directional attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,she learned the responses, the abilities, \Nand the defensive capabilities of each type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, in an instant, she was able \Nto calculate which armor to use
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,against each kind of monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her attacking power has improved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Wing Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With each strike, its power increases!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she's starting out by reducing \Ntheir numbers with sheer force, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It breathes fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! If the enemy's fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! She's \Ngot Flame Empress Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She brushed the flames aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A weapon that's part of a set \Nwith her Sea Empress Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water against flames, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! She's destroyed five \NC-class monsters already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fire and water dual-sword technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it also looks like \Nshe took some damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're S-class...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She returned fire against the water enemy \Nwith Sea Empress Armor and a lightning attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the confidence to back it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a wonderful wizard, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already cut down half of the monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Erza for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her every move is polished, \Nwith not a movement wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sho and Wally \Nare watching, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really anything \Nto make a fuss about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her! She's all beat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look like she's exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:29.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Erza! Smash 'em to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's kind \Nof having a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:53.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy! Even wounded, Erza smoothly \Ndispatched a succession of monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but now she's facing an A-class monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That looked like a heavy hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Hit that badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:08.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Just the opposite. I \Nbelieve she used its weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The terrifying Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She requips over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,steadily crushing the monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While she's taken damage and \Ndepleted a lot of her magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,unbelievably... just four monsters are left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But those are all strong ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And she hasn't defeated \Nthe S-class monster yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-class, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know just how awesome S-class Erza is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally... And finally, the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:13.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of monster is an S-class one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the S-class, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute monster-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I have a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why is Erza-nee changing her sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Benizakura to two swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Against that puny foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must be up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Look at her expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her concentration and sense \Nof tension have doubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:02.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you \Nit was impossible-kabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's set up so that when the S-class monster
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:10.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,becomes the last one left, \Nits power triples-kabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Pandemonium's last monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:18.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow the battle \Nhas moved to the arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The now super-sized S-class \Nmonster is bearing down on Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew they set it up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An unexpected ambush...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Fitting for a place \Ncalled "Pandemonium"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! That giant thing is \Nno match for you, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The third day of the Grand Magic Games...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandemonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll ever forget this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while being badly wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a fairy that should've \Nfallen to the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...soared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:34.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dignified scarlet \Nflower in all its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:49.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly, Erza has obliterated \N100 monsters all by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet of Fairy Tail A has \Nscored a resounding victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without any question, a tremendous win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the true strength of the guild \Nthat was called the most powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,seven years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's strongest \Nwoman wizard, Erza Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Titania! Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cheering just won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her rash action...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see that it would lead to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It took longer than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lump in my throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... It's not like \Nwe won the tournament yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:02.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it took longer \Nthan you thought it would?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody holds a candle to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er-chan really is the most powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spiffiest and most powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've expected no less \Nof Ichiya-san's girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She blazes as brightly as the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess seeing that makes \Na guy say reckless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Erza! Erza! Erza! Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Erza! Erza! Erza! Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Erza! Erza! Erza! Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail has been booed since day one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this wild applause makes \Nthat almost hard to believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing her, anybody would applaud...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was moved as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven years that were lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I don't have \Nto worry about it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:14:00.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's no big deal! We \Ncould've done the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fro thinks so, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you aren't all talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they don't call her \N"Titania" for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Jellal well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandemonium has been conquered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:31.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail A receives ten points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After some discussion, it's been decided \Nthat the other seven teams need to be ranked,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so this is somewhat of a drag, but \Na simple game has been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Power Finder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:52.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, MPF!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:55.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A device to measure magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:15:02.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When this machine is hit with magic, the \Nmagic power will be displayed as a numeral value.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those values will be \Nranked, from high to low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple test of strength, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at kind of a disadvantage here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Cana-san, are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:19.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free, but I don't think I'll be \Nable to drink more than one barrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You drink too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an understatement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:31.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana-san! The competition isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with the order that \Nwas decided before-kabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:39.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Under the cloak is a daring outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitten Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:51.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The value is 365!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that being said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,without a benchmark to compare it to, we \Ndon't know if this is a high score or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:05.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We Rune Knights also use the \NMPF as part of our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This number is a high score.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A level high enough to \Nmake someone a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's an impressive figure, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' spiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Millianna's real \Nstrength isn't about power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be at a disadvantage here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Quatro Puppy's Novale!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:28.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His value is 124! Seems a little low...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tough one for Hibiki, whose \Nmagic is the intellectual type.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've done this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your friend, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:42.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're back in action, huh, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jenny passed me the baton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki of Blue Pegasus! \NHis magic power is 95...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what we get for believing in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:04.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men... But there's a lot \Nto learn from failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take this and strive \Nto do better, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Your words are sweet \Nmusic to our ears, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already striving...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Want me to comfort you tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I want you to baby me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is Obra of Raven Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...who attacked Carla and Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raven, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of magic he'll use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! His magic power is 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he just messin' around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And shouldn't you be in the infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:47.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little unfortunate, but \Nthere are no do-overs here-kabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Obra, what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His magic can't be shown in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a guy who's gotta \Nbe forced to get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,currently the top score is 365 from \NMillianna of Mermaid Heel-kabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'm number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:22.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabertooth's Orga takes the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to those cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Orga-kun! Please win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Orga's strong, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:33.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,120mm Black Lightning Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Over 3,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten times my score?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a score like \Nthat, not even in my Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Orga-kun! When it comes \Nto power, he's the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fro thinks so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:00.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The strongest, the strongest, number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to hear \Nany more singing-kabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Our guild, Sabertooth, kicks \Nthe ass of everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, can Jura, one of the 10 Great \NWizard Saints, surpass this score?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got everyone's attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura-san will win, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'm concerned \Nabout something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I do this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead-kabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:25.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Jura of Lamia \NScale is concentrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're feeling tremendous pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumbling Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:46.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,8,544! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, that's wack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In a word, unsurprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those nicknamed the 10 Great Wizard Saints
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:59.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,are just so powerful. Shouldn't \Ntheir participation be limited?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's what you're \Nworried about, Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is a new record for the MPF!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The title "10 Great Wizard \NSaints" isn't just for show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This blows me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:14.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably evenly matched with Gildarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that someone who shares \NGildarts' blood is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And our final challenger is \NCana Alberona of Fairy Tail B!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's finally my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:32.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's tough to follow Jura, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just do your best-kabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she gonna try to get into \Nthe thousands in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I predict in the high hundreds \Nfor a third place finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she stripping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm gonna hit you hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That emblem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lent it to her just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so she could win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:03.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:07.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,River of light that guides fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, that woman
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,has incredibly high latent ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sure she'll be able to master this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine! To destroy the fangs of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:23.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Glitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Cana possesses one of the \NThree Great Fairy Magics?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:33.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The MPF is destroyed! The counter's stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guild?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one-two finish for \Nthe competition part!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:46.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone stop Fairy Tail now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:52.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we're Fairy Tail, see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think a bit-kabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alexei-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the list of battle matches...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This match-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The management is well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of our true purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:58.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Feelin' spiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:03.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought up a Mini Anna cheer song!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.70,0:24:06.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, it's "Millianna", not "Mini Anna"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's on a rival team!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I could go on, but \Nfirst off, why a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.87,0:24:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of cheering the usual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Laxus vs. Alexei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the king of crackling lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.66,0:24:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that's your \Ncheer song for Laxus?!
